879	// uapiConfig renders cfg into the newline-delimited UAPI set string the engine's
880	// IpcSet consumes. Keys are lowercase hex (UAPI's on-the-wire encoding), NOT the
881	// base64 form the TOML carries. Amnezia obfuscation keys are emitted only when the
882	// block is configured; an all-zero Amnezia block leaves the engine in plain
